msgid ""
"<b>GitHub Releases (recommended):</b>\n"
"Click the button next to Update URL to fill with template, then edit OWNER/REPO\n"
"\n"
"<b>Example:</b>\n"
"https://api.github.com/repos/biglinux/big-video-converter/releases/latest\n"
"\n"
"<b>Filename Pattern:</b>\n"
"Used to identify which file to download from the release.\n"
"The asterisk (*) matches any text.\n"
"\n"
"<b>Pattern Examples:</b>\n"
"• myapp-*-x86_64.AppImage  → matches: myapp-v1.2.3-x86_64.AppImage\n"
"• *-gui-*.AppImage  → matches: converter-gui-1.0.AppImage\n"
"• calculator-*.AppImage  → matches: calculator-2.5-linux.AppImage"
msgstr ""
"<b>GitHub Vydania (odporúčané):</b>\n"
"Kliknite na tlačidlo vedľa Aktualizovať URL, aby ste vyplnili šablónu, potom upravte VLASTNÍK/REPO\n"
"\n"
"<b>Príklad:</b>\n"
"https://api.github.com/repos/biglinux/big-video-converter/releases/latest\n"
"\n"
"<b>Vzorec názvu súboru:</b>\n"
"Používa sa na identifikáciu, ktorý súbor sa má stiahnuť z vydania.\n"
"Hvezdička (*) zodpovedá akémukoľvek textu.\n"
"\n"
"<b>Príklady vzorov:</b>\n"
"• myapp-*-x86_64.AppImage  → zodpovedá: myapp-v1.2.3-x86_64.AppImage\n"
"• *-gui-*.AppImage  → zodpovedá: converter-gui-1.0.AppImage\n"
"• calculator-*.AppImage  → zodpovedá: calculator-2.5-linux.AppImage"
